## Dictionary method 

-------------------------------------------------------------------

## Key

m1  --> pd1{"Level" : 45}

m2  --> pd2 --> pd1.keys   ## pd2 = pd1.keys stored all the keys of pd1

m3  --> 45                 ## pd2 = 45

--------------------------------------------------------------------

## Update  

m1 ---> sm {"name" : "Sameer Barde"}

m2 ---> sm.update({"Age" : "28"})   ##sm.update() updates the original Dictionary

m3 ---> sm name : Sameer Barde, Age : 28        # sm returns the dictionary with updated values